descriptionHtml:
All your conversation in one place

What can you do with Wspace?
- Have one on one chat with your friends and colleagues.
- Create unlimited channels.
- Invite anyone into your channel.
- Create task assignment, meeting invitation and poll
- And many more

Having trouble? Please contact admin@wspace.io
descriptionShort: All your conversation in one place
title: Wspace

creator: Infomina Sdn Bhd
descriptionHtml:
Wspace is a collaboration app for businesses and organisations to initiate and keep track their day to day tasks and activities. Features that Wspace offers are:

- Group Chat; keep in touch with team without limited users.
- Invite, accept and decline meeting (Meeting Invitation in Chat)
- Assign task to team
- Get responses from team (Follow Up)
- Create a survey or a questionnaire (Poll)
- Send file attachment
- Respond to a message privately
- Remind other users not to miss a task before deadline
- Pin important messages to make it easier to find
- Quote certain messages to reply
- Stickers!! to create fun conversation
- Search specific users within contacts, channel name or hashtag (Searching)
- Submit actions for pending tasks
- Send a like to a message
- Get people attention by mentioning them (@ mention)
- Add & remove users from channel
- Close channel
- View user's response time
- Assign hashtags to channels to make searching easier
- Archive closed channel to hide from channel list
- Direct Message; Communicate in private space between two person.
- View contacts online status
- Trophy Leaderboard; earn hidden trophies by executing day-to-day activities on the app and keep track the trophy leaderboard.
descriptionShort: All your conversation in one place
